# filePresenters

**Type Property**

Returns an array containing the currently registered file presenter objects.

## Declaration

```swift
class var filePresenters: [any NSFilePresenter] { get }
```

## Return Value

An array of objects that conform to the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSFilePresenter] protocol.

## Managing File Presenters

- **addFilePresenter(_:)**: Registers the specified file presenter object so that it can receive notifications.
- **removeFilePresenter(_:)**: Unregisters the specified file presenter object.
- **purposeIdentifier**: A string that uniquely identifies the file access that was performed by this file coordinator.
